<br>
I noticed that there is a second specialized quest that goes beyond the Planar Travelers Manual quest.<br>
<br>
** Note ** this was pure speculation on my part.  The Quest NPC is one of the sage's apprentices.  The quest seems entirely different from the spell research quest we are focusing on here.  This quest also involves traditional tradeskills.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/quests/pop_aftermanual.htm">www.eqtraders.com/quests/...manual.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
In short, once you obtain the Travelers Handbook, you can show it to an NPC and go down one of three quests for a specialized book - Magic, Stealth, or one last one that hasnt been solved yet apparently.<br>
<br>
Now that the first part of the spell research quest seems to have been fleshed out, I have doubts that this Basic Magic Manual quest has anything to do with the Spell Research quest (but you never know).  Also note that the quest seems to be bugged at this time.<br>
