ane of Justice</span><hr size=1> You know the Enforcer halls where you did one of the trials for PoV. The Enforcers and Punishers were dropping PArchments farely commonly. I was there 7 hours running various Groups from my Guild and over the 7 hours close to 20 dropped. We controlled the whole hall keeping it clear as they spawned. Keep in mind the faster you kill the more often they pop. More often they pop the higher likely hood they will drop the parchments. <br>
