<br>
You know that you can turn 4 of these notes in for 4 different items with charges.<br>
<br>
WHY aren't you extracting the charges OFF those items?????<br>
<br>
Quest 1:  Extract these notes out of these spells. Turn this in and get a charged ITEM!!!!!!! and a QUILL!!!!!!!<br>
<br>
Quest 2:  Extract spell effects and bindings out of items that have Magic Effects. (Probably requires quill *cough cough*, some sort of parchment *something to write on*, charged item, and POSSIBLY somethingelse.<br>
<br>
Quest 3:  Combine runes and words for something. *wistles* POSSIBLY, combining the extracted bindings (runes) and extracted effects (words), together to make either a spell or something to turn in to one of quest 1's apprentices.<br>
<br>
These quests are related, they MIGHT each be seperate in SOME regards, but they are RELATED.  It is a triangle quest with a Potential for 45 different outcomes.  3 NPC's as self quests + 3 circles of quests (meaning all 3 NPC's) + 3 bilateral quests for 2 of said NPC's + 5 Notes, or 5 items, or 5 ect, depending on which route you take = 45.  Notes=items=3rd quest things, they are 1 since they match up.<br>
<br>
There are 2 assistants for each questgiver.  1 assistant is gem+xp, the other assistant is XXXXXX. (this would also give you 45 ways to get xp and gem, but thats mute). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=noonievioletskies>NoonieVioletskies</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1314<br> <font color=#333333>(10/28/02 5:11:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=178>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ..</span><hr size=1> a good place to get level 39 spells to do the notes is to farm sirens in cs, as i found out when doing my shawl quest.<br>
